    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">6. Acceptable use</h2>
    <p>You agree not to misuse the Service, including by: attempting to access another member's chart or data; probing, scanning, or testing the vulnerability of the system; interfering with or disrupting the Service; uploading malicious code; scraping or harvesting data; or using the Service for any unlawful purpose. Secure messaging is for communication with your care team only and must not be used to harass or abuse.</p>

